{"comments":"Levels Effect — Industry-standard levels color correction.\n\n## Industry Standard\n\nMirrors AE's Levels effect with per-channel control:\n\n- **Input Black/White**: Remaps input range (0.0-1.0, clamps)\n- **Gamma**: Midtone adjustment (0.1-10.0, clamps)\n- **Output Black/White**: Remaps output range (0.0-1.0, clamps)\n\nEach channel (Master, Red, Green, Blue, Alpha) has independent controls.\n\n## Properties (All Animatable)\n\n| Property | Type | Min | Max | Behavior | Default |\n|----------|------|-----|-----|----------|---------|\n| inputBlack | Number | 0.0 | 1.0 | clamps | 0.0 |\n| inputWhite | Number | 0.0 | 1.0 | clamps | 1.0 |\n| gamma | Number | 0.1 | 10.0 | clamps | 1.0 |\n| outputBlack | Number | 0.0 | 1.0 | clamps | 0.0 |\n| outputWhite | Number | 0.0 | 1.0 | clamps | 1.0 |\n\n## GPU Shader\n\n```glsl\nfloat applyLevels(float v, float inBlack, float inWhite, float gamma, float outBlack, float outWhite) {\n  float normalized = clamp((v - inBlack) / (inWhite - inBlack), 0.0, 1.0);\n  float gammaCorrected = pow(normalized, 1.0 / gamma);\n  return outBlack + gammaCorrected * (outWhite - outBlack);\n}\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["inputBlack",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Percentage"],"Ratio"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["inputWhite",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Percentage"],"Ratio"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["gamma",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Effects","ColorCorrection","Levels"],"LevelsGamma"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["outputBlack",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Percentage"],"Ratio"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["outputWhite",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Percentage"],"Ratio"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[123,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/Levels.purs","start":[117,23]},"title":"ChannelLevels"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Effects","ColorCorrection","Levels"],"ChannelLevels"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[125,52],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/Levels.purs","start":[125,1]},"title":"eqChannelLevels"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Effects","ColorCorrection","Levels"],"ChannelLevels"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[131,76],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/Levels.purs","start":[127,1]},"title":"showChannelLevels"}],"comments":"Levels settings for a single channel.\n\nAll properties are animatable.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[123,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Motion/Effects/ColorCorrection/Levels.purs","start":[117,1]},"title":"ChannelLevels"},{"children":[],"comments":"Default channel levels (no adjustment).\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Motion","Effects","ColorCorrection","Levels"],"ChannelLevels"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"ki